casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 533 U. S. 946.]

Motion of the River Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $2,970.18 for the period April 1 through June 30, 2001, to be paid equally by the parties.
